                In China, there was graduate girl who dyed her hair pink commiting suicide under the pressure of online gossip; but there also exists woman fighting against unfair family role under the support of net people. Many women fight for rebuilding images; some failed, some succeeded. <mark>However, only making tries more, making the trace of women's battle more emphasized can we let people know women are far more than just sex, face, and supplemental income source.</mark>
            </h3>
